short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension was designed for professors. It provides them with tools that ease the tasks related to managing the participants

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Manage your meetings like a pro with this extension for professors. You can easily record, export, and share the participation of your members in csv files. You can also create polls, reply to messages, roll a dice, and more!

Learn what meet participants manager can do for you at
https://meetsparticipantsmanager.wordpress.com/
